Package: pkgaudit
Title: Security Auditing of R Packages
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tyler", "Smith", , "tylerjssmith@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for security auditing of R packages. Detects 
    dangerous patterns in R source code using XPath-based rules stored in a
    versioned and hash-verified SQLite database.
